 66→ * Onboarding overlay with Agent Dots intro animation.
 67→ *
 68→ * Sequence:
 69→ *   1. Semi-transparent dark overlay fades in over the desktop
 70→ *   2. Agent Dots play on transparent bg (dots float over overlay)
 71→ *   3. Animation fades out during "The Pull" (~7-8s)
 72→ *   4. Card fades in → user navigates steps
 73→ *   5. Complete → exit animation → overlay dissolves → window restores
 74→ *
 75→ * Window architecture (Electron):
 76→ *   - Main window renders everything fullscreen
 77→ *   - Transparent background with vibrancy for macOS
 78→ */
